text: Bredael is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Alexander van Bredael (1663–1720), Flemish painter *Annelies Bredael (born 1965), Belgian rower *Jan Frans van Bredael (1686–1750), Flemish painter *Jan Pieter van Bredael the Younger (1683–1735), Flemish painter *Joris van Bredael (1661–c. 1706), Flemish painter *Joseph van Bredael (1688–1739), Flemish painter *Peeter van Bredael (1629–1719), Flemish painter ==References==
